http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/Tour-other-States-Mulayam-tells-Akhilesh/article14014962.ece

Samajwadi Party supremo Mulayam Singh on Friday advised son and Uttar Pradesh Chief Minister Akhilesh Yadav to tour others States and hold rallies there in order to become a “big leader”.“If you want to become big leader, you should tour other states also. Go and hold rallies in Bihar, Uttrakahand and Madhya Pradesh. Now a days there are a lot of facilities available, helicopter can be used for travelling.“People consider SP as a regional party...” Mulayam said while pointing at Akhilesh.Mulayam was addressing a gathering on the occasion of the death anniversary of party leader Janeshwar Mishra here. - PTI